dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Roads_2015.gdb. [This data represents the Waupaca County transportation network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are geocoded with a address range.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. Best available date of this dataset 5/12/2015. For online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.waupaca.wi.us/landinformation/Data.aspx.
